{"lastModified":1772745422134,"uri":"c::9861085442::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nExplore the ancient wonders of the Adriatic coast with Lupus Mare. At 43m in length with 10 crew members, she offers outstanding service and overnight accommodation for up to 34 guests. Built in 2011 by Brodosplit, she underwent a refit in 2018, followed by a further refit in 2022 (due to be completed in April 2023) during which technical aspects of the yacht are being modernized, including the introduction of an impressive brand-new cinema, jacuzzi, gym and sauna.\n\nThe perfect option for larger groups looking to explore Croatia’s glittering coastline and islands, guests can spend their days soaking up history, culture, and sampling spectacular food. She features a fantastic range of onboard water toys and equipment including snorkeling and fishing equipment, inflatable water slide, jetski, SUPS, kayaks, Seabob and more.\n\nLupus Mare’s large sundeck is the ultimate place for relaxation and soaking up the sun, featuring a generous amount of space and plenty of sun loungers. After a day of diving in the ocean and sunbathing, guests will now have the option to head down to the sauna and unwind ahead of dinner.\n\nInside, the saloon, dining and lounge area is located on the upper deck, where guests can dine, socialize, and enjoy bar service.\n\nAccommodation comprises of 15 ultra-modern and stylish en-suite cabins. These consist of six double cabins, two twins and two triple cabins on the main deck. The lower deck features two double, one twin and two triple cabins. All cabins are airconditioned with hairdryers, Starlink WIFI and safes, and all have their own private shower en-suite. There are also two day heads located throughout the rest of the yacht. \n\nThe brand-new gym features a great range of workout equipment, including yoga mats, Pilates balls, TRX bands, dumbbells and jumping ropes, ensuring fitness conscious guests are well catered for throughout their charter.","blueprint":{"name":"LUPUS MARE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c4984710-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c5443e80-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c40c81d0-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c6992020-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c5f90f90-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ca233140-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c74f02a0-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c7f9e8a0-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c8bac7a0-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::cd6d2c20-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::cad67bb0-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c9708310-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e9be2a50-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974eaebb841c.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3aa-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::cba98320-fdc6-11ee-97a5-974ea